接口 mcfppListener

所有超级接口:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
所有已知实现类:
mcfppBaseListener, McfppImListener
public interface mcfppListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by mcfppParser.
